creator: Flying Nugget
descriptionHtml: In this classic automation game, you are tasked with giving life to a number of cells, who will then replicate based on a set of mathematical rules. If done correctly, you can turn a small amount of live cells into a giant organism in order to reach the objective of the game.
descriptionShort: A puzzle pattern matching game based on Conway's Game of Life

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: More functionality, easier access to levels etc.
